OL,5, Four MPs are being asked to repay      
OL,6, hundreds of pounds in driving fines    
OL,7, which they claimed on expenses.        
OL,9,FGovernment minister Amanda Solloway    
OL,10,Fclaimed an #80 fixed penalty notice    
OL,11,Fissued by Transport for London in 2020.
OL,13,FTory MPs Simon Hoare and Bim Afolami,  
OL,14,Fand SNP MP Dave Doogan, also put       
OL,15,Fthrough similar claims.                
OL,17,FMPs are not allowed to claim for fines 
OL,18,Fand some were wrongfully paid out, but 
OL,19,Fat least one MP is understood to have  
OL,20,Falready paid back the money.           
